::Ramulus::

Seeing that Dinobot has the raptor situation under controlls, Ramulus returns 
to Shadow Cat and Snow Tech.

"Sorry about the interruption," he says several seconds before recieving 
Stegotron's distress call. He sighs.

"Duty calls. Want to come?" he asks the two new bots as he runs off toward 
the battle.

"I'm on my way, Stegotron," he says into his comm-link while running.
